item.title: about
item.description: Hi! My name is Jay. I make a living as a programmer, but I’m now seriously considering doing music after all of the weird turn of events in my life. I’ve never written a blog before, so bare with me as I share with you the journey I have in battling this thing called cancer. It’s not the greatest, but it’s not the worst. I’m fearfully made by God, and I really hope that my story encourages your faith in Christ Jesus.
